text:
You know, it never came up! 
For the most part, these places are not BYOD. The users are not admins, and all
DNS points to the DCs or router. Any resolving is forwarded from there. That
will deal with more cases, but clearly not all. – I’ll have to talk to the
network people. 
Thanks,
Shimon
